            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>The Ottawa South Community Centre is nestled in the heart of Old Ottawa South. The centre offers a wide variety of recreation programs in partnership with the Ottawa South Community Association.</p>
<p>Please visit the <a href="https://oldottawasouth.ca/">Old Ottawa South Community Association&nbsp;website</a> to view their programs.</p>
<p>A variety of rooms at Ottawa South Community Centre can be rented through the City of Ottawa. Whether it is a meeting, children’s birthday party or a small wedding we can help with your rental needs.</p>
